### 📄 List all files in Google Drive
GET http://localhost:3000/api/google-drive/getAll

### 🌐 Upload a file from an external URL
POST http://localhost:3000/api/google-drive/upload-from-url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://github.com/fgp555.png"
}

