### 🗑️ Delete a file from Google Drive
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/google-drive/1Jl1W60ECbD_GaeKA2lBEKO7HR_NZip2R


### ✏️ Rename a file in Google Drive
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/google-drive/1Jl1W60ECbD_GaeKA2lBEKO7HR_NZip2R
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "renamed-image.png"
}

### 📤 Upload a file (basic upload)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/google-drive/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello, this is a test file.
--MyBoundary--


### 📤 Upload a file with name and description
POST http://localhost:3000/api/google-drive/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

my-file
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

my-description
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="README.md"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ../README.md
--MyBoundary--




